WEBVTT

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:09.220
Even thoughble land is being destroyed

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:44.000
The sake of the world is not to be drunk

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:55.000
If you drink it, you will be a man

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:13.000
Is there a sound waiting for me on the back street of the moon?

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:46.000
The long road is short

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:58.000
That is what it is called

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:03.000
One drop of Makoto, one drop of Doko

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:10.000
One drop of Himizu, one drop of Doko

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:16.000
One drop of Himizu, one drop of Doko

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:38.000
Translated by Releska

